translation[9]{c,v,t}:
  34,23,Intethelelo ayinakunceda bani kuYe. Ngaphandle kwalowo Amvumeleyo
  34,24,"(Kananjalo abo bayalinda) de kudambe uvalo ezintliziyweni zabo. Baya kuthi (omnye komnye): “Itheni na: iNkosi yenu?” (baphendule) bona bathi: ‘Yinyaniso.’ Yaye Yona nguSobunganga Omkhulu.’” Yithi: “Ngubani onondlayo emazulwini nasemhlabeni? Yithi: “nguAllâh.” Inene sithi okanye nini abaphantsi kwesiKhokelo okanye ekulahlekeni okucacileyo!”"
  34,25,"Yithi: Nina aniyi kubuzwa ngoko kwenziwe Sithi; kanti nathi asiyi kubuzwa ngoko nikwenzayo.”"
  34,26,"Yithi: “INkosi yethu Iza kusihlanganisa sonke, Ize Igwebe phakathi kwethu ngenyaniso. Yaye Yona nguMgwebi Owaziyo.”"
  34,27,"Yithi: Ndiboniseni kaloku abo nibayamanise naYe njengamahlulelane. Nakanye! Ukusuka apho Yena (uYedwa) nguAllâh, uSobunganga, uSobulumko.”"
  34,28,"Asikuthumelelanga ukuba ube yinto yimbi ngaphandle kokubaubenguMvakalisiweendabaezilungileyonoMlumkisi ebantwini bonke, kodwa uninzi lwabantu alwazi"
  34,29,"Ke kaloku bathi: “Siya kuba nini na esi sithembiso, ukuba nithetha inyaniso?”"
  34,30,"Yithi wena: “Okwenu yiMini ekhethiweyo, Eningayi kuyibambezela nangeyure enye, ningayi kuyandulela nokuyandulela.”"
  34,31,"Ke kaloku abo bangakholwayo bathi: “Asisokuze sikholwe kule ‘Kur’ân singasokuze (sikholwe) nakuloo (Ncwadi ingaphambili kunayo.” Kodwa ukuba ubunokubabona abenzi bobubi xa beya kumiswa phambi kweNkosi yabo, bephikisana iintetho zabo. Abo babecinezelekile baya kuthi kwabo babekhukhumele: “Ukuba kwakungekho ngenxa yenu ngesasibe ngamakholwa (amaMuslim)!”"